===Format===
* '''League Stage''' : ''June 9th-10th
** 27 teams divided equally into 3 groups of 9.
** Round-robin format.
** {{bgcolortext|up|Top 16}} teams qualify for finals.

* '''Finals''' : ''June 11th-12th
** 16 teams , 2 matchdays.
** 10 matches (5 each day).

